# ============================================================================
# Sally Sells — .env.example
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to ⁠ .env ⁠ and fill in the real secrets. The real .env is
# gitignored. Every variable used anywhere in the backend or voice agent is
# listed here — if a new one is introduced, add it to this file too.
# ============================================================================

